{"tid":1036974,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"法唔法國鳩噏係一件好減壓嘅事","createTime":"2019-02-25T15:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T04:51:46.000Z","uid":137339,"like":62,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"db9f6e52dbcae7e7b81c90c00ed337224c0f500c","tid":1036974,"uid":137339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:10:45.000Z","msg":"人類嘅本性就係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而我地表現得正常係因為社會嘅規範，禮儀之類嘅限制。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似係冇人見到嘅時候，我地係會有衝動做啲戇鳩野 。而我地嘅大腦更加係會出現好多戇鳩想法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而鳩噏就係一種人類本能。而做釋放本能嘅事，係會得到快感，因為咁樣係會啓動人體嘅獎勵機制（好似做愛咁）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我地嘅身體係會獎勵我地跟隨本性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而鳩噏就係以語言去表達戇鳩思想，係一種人類文明嘅體現，一種高等嘅人文藝術。<br />\n<br />\n鳩噏真係好撚正。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：9upper"},{"pid":"9c0b48d9861a183dae8350922a75343feebe4bb3","tid":1036974,"uid":182556,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔覺"},{"pid":"375c9805cd4734f74cb7381f8392572a5128e052","tid":1036974,"uid":137339,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9c0b48d9861a183dae8350922a75343feebe4bb3","tid":1036974,"uid":182556,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"920da2c9ac6f3ea27dc3b9339e94027af251dcb8","tid":1036974,"uid":168384,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"勝在up完冇人知你up乜<br />\n講野唔洗認真"},{"pid":"2197f69679e7883ed71267523b17a0bf1f9b4cef","tid":1036974,"uid":6783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"0be008aff01d44d08f297abc80741630d5a16e8a","tid":1036974,"uid":43804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"